:"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"2771320873","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2771320873","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjc3MTMyMDg3Mw==","status":"current","title":"App de Comercios","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":465},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2771320873/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2771320873/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2771320873/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2771320873/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2771320873","tinyui":"/x/KQAvpQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2771320873","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2771320873/App+de+Comercios","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2771320873"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"0cf2b2d9-c211-405d-82ed-60ec7b0ac012\"><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Pregunta</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Resp</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Vamos a querer poder ver las notificaciones en la app? Quieren priorzar esto? </p><p>En el caso de que si, habr&iacute;a que haber un desarrollo en el back para poder enviarlas</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Revisar si todas las opciones del <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/B2OegwDelZT3W0HJ1biJTa/-HANDOFF--App---Adquirencia?node-id=11585-9633&amp;t=bM8Fy21Gozpg1mVB-4\">men&uacute;</a> est&aacute;n implementados en la app</p></td><td><p>Faltan:</p><ul><li><p>Facturaci&oacute;n electr&oacute;nica</p></li><li><p>Dispositivos seguros</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/B2OegwDelZT3W0HJ1biJTa/-HANDOFF--App---Adquirencia?node-id=11607-294&amp;t=bM8Fy21Gozpg1mVB-4\">Carga de documentos en HOME</a> &rarr; Que pasa al momento de subir el documento? Tendr&iacute;amos que tener una vista que informe al usuario que su solicitud est&aacute; siendo procesada?</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Revisar desde donde hacemos el conteo de los intentos de login y de bloqueado de usuario</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>En la secci&oacute;n de cobrar con tarjeta hay que tener en cuenta el tema de permisos, merchant id, table device.</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Falta vista de <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/B2OegwDelZT3W0HJ1biJTa/-HANDOFF--App---Adquirencia?node-id=11585-6319&amp;t=289yiTaAz7QYpc4h-4\">empty state para dispositivos seguros</a></p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>En la vista de <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/B2OegwDelZT3W0HJ1biJTa/-HANDOFF--App---Adquirencia?node-id=11585-11704&amp;t=289yiTaAz7QYpc4h-4\">seleccionar sucursal para realizar un cobro</a>, deber&iacute;amos agregar un buscador</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Es necesario <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/B2OegwDelZT3W0HJ1biJTa/-HANDOFF--App---Adquirencia?node-id=11585-11704&amp;t=289yiTaAz7QYpc4h-4\">este</a> paso? No es mejor que seleccione automaticamente la sucursal por defecto</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Tenemos que generar un pdf de <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/B2OegwDelZT3W0HJ1biJTa/-HANDOFF--App---Adquirencia?node-id=11585-11990&amp;t=289yiTaAz7QYpc4h-4\">estos comprobantes?</a> O compartimos directamente la vista como captura?</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Falta vista cuando falla el env&iacute;o de una factura o est&aacute; ca&iacute;do TaxiIT</p><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/B2OegwDelZT3W0HJ1biJTa/-HANDOFF--App---Adquirencia?node-id=11585-12538&amp;t=Sb2uuxNchVFre0v0-4\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://www.figma.com/design/B2OegwDelZT3W0HJ1biJTa/-HANDOFF--App---Adquirencia?node-id=11585-12538&amp;t=Sb2uuxNchVFre0v0-4</a></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Vamos a poder filtrar las transferencias en la secci&oacute;n de movimientos?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/B2OegwDelZT3W0HJ1biJTa/-HANDOFF--App---Adquirencia?node-id=11585-15837&amp;t=Sb2uuxNchVFre0v0-4\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://www.figma.com/design/B2OegwDelZT3W0HJ1biJTa/-HANDOFF--App---Adquirencia?node-id=11585-15837&amp;t=Sb2uuxNchVFre0v0-4</a></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>[Movimientos] Vamos a ver el detalle de las transferencias / acreditaciones</p><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/B2OegwDelZT3W0HJ1biJTa/-HANDOFF--App---Adquirencia?node-id=11585-15837&amp;t=RwEW7ZPqZgUHX19T-4\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://www.figma.com/design/B2OegwDelZT3W0HJ1biJTa/-HANDOFF--App---Adquirencia?node-id=11585-15837&amp;t=RwEW7ZPqZgUHX19T-4</a></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/4199743504"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":1136},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4199743504/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4199743504/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4199743504/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4199743504/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=4199743504","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4199743504/Preguntas+Redise+o+App+de+Comercios","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/4199743504","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4199743504","tinyui":"/x/EABT_g","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}